  div.main_slider.contentsmargin
    -
      var items = [
        {
          itemNum: 1,
          itemName: 'cat-green'
        },
        {
          itemNum: 2,
          itemName: 'cat-coral'
        }
      ]
    each item in items
      div.main_slider-item
        figure
          img(src="./img/index/key0"+item['itemNum']+".jpg" alt="")
        div.main_slider-info.contain
          p.main_slider-name
            span.main_slider-cat(class=item['itemName']) 婚活アプリ
            span.main_slider-date 2019.05.08
          p.main_slider-text 【令和元年】ぶっちゃけどの婚活アプリが熱いの？⼈気アプリ10社を徹底比較！
